query: WITH entities AS (SELECT telegram_id, id FROM core_customers WHERE (COALESCE((telegram_id, id) < ($3, $2), $2 IS NULL)) ORDER BY telegram_id DESC, id DESC LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: CustomerId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_customer_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.telegram_id desc, i.id desc, i.id, e.sequence
